{"tid":1911432,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【學術討論】因為武肺全世界都開始\"排華反中\"，香港人係咪都應該加入戰團？","createTime":"2020-03-05T10:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T17:28:42.000Z","uid":293677,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"304dbac23cf26680295700606e72071dd120a494","tid":1911432,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYJDKd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYJDKd6.png&h=0356108c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PRrmN4YzPP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPRrmN4YzPP4&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=36cd0427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PRrmN4YzPP4</a><br />\n<br />\n因為中国輸出&quot;武漢病毒&quot;<br />\n搞到西方文明國家都歧視所有亞洲人黃種人<br />\n依家亞洲國家都對中国人都出現敵意<br />\n即係全世界都&quot;反中&quot;<br />\n喺呢個關鍵時機<br />\n香港人係咪都應該加入世界潮流一齊反支那人?<br />\n<br />\n商店唔接待支那人?<br />\n見到支那人就屌鳩佢地?<br />\n支那人唔戴口罩就召喚神獸?<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇??<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：本POST只係學術討論，本人反對一切種族歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329e05d19657615b6d18306e60c40cae7fc4c2fa","tid":1911432,"uid":165665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:18:20.000Z","msg":"香港人太善良"},{"pid":"8e8505535d4fae785f501628a03a6cf29a2c90fd","tid":1911432,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"係，推到全球反支<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff7bfb124614531d2502bed36d052d2260a44273","tid":1911432,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:22:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af7dea9e32ef300e8d32cbb920894aab9ab4c3d0","tid":1911432,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b7f1f7b829d87b8b27a0845dd6722d00ec4879e","tid":1911432,"uid":67444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T17:28:42.000Z","msg":"值得討論"}]}